response.original_title: Yung Beef es un GENIO: El Documental
response.overview: A documentary about Yung Beef, tracing his journey from the underground scene to his cultural impact in Spanish trap music. Through personal stories, performances and reflections, the film explores his life, artistic vision, and the turbulent path that shaped his legacy.
response.tagline: Yung Beef is a genius… and today i’ll explain why
response.title: Yung Beef es un GENIO: El Documental
